#Divination Grok

Here's a fully functional **HTML + CSS + JavaScript prototype** for your divination game exactly as you described. It works in any modern browser, requires no backend, and includes:

- Daily horoscope (based on zodiac sign)  
- Tarot card (random major arcana)  
- I Ching hexagram (coin method)  
- Combination logic ‚Üí one of four signs: **Love ‚ù§Ô∏è**, **Fortune üí∞**, **Fame ‚≠ê**, **Adventure üó∫Ô∏è**  
- Personalization form (zodiac + birth date for tarot moon sign + name for flavor)  
- Persistent storage via `localStorage` so settings survive refresh  
- Mobile-friendly, beautiful gradient design  

Just save this as `index.html` and open it.

```html
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
